branchCategory.name: XSA
branchCategory.description: <p>Series XSA is a normally closed solenoid valve suitable for air or inert gas in high vacuum applications.  This valve functions properly at an operating pressure as low as 1x10<sup>-6</sup> Pa(absolute).  Face Seal and compression fitting options offer extremely low levels of internal and external leakage.  Two DC and eight AC voltage options are available, paired with multiple electrical entry styles.</p>
